# ChangeLog for <dev-libs>/<libanssipki-crypto>

  01 Dec 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  libanssipki-crypto-2.1.1.ebuild:
  Add masked amd64 keyword.

*libanssipki-crypto-2.1.1 (02 Mar 2015)

  02 Mar 2015; Piotr Chmielnicki <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.1.1.ebuild, -libanssipki-crypto-2.1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Cleanly fixed parallel compilation

*libanssipki-crypto-2.1.0-r1 (25 Feb 2015)

  25 Feb 2015; Piotr Chmielnicki <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.1.0-r1.ebuild, -libanssipki-crypto-2.1.0.ebuild:
  Fixed compile bug

*libanssipki-crypto-2.1.0 (23 Feb 2015)

  23 Feb 2015; Piotr Chmielnicki <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.1.0.ebuild, -libanssipki-crypto-2.0.2.ebuild:
  Added the anssipki-genrsa tool

*libanssipki-crypto-2.0.2 (11 Feb 2015)

  11 Feb 2015; Piotr Chmielnicki <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.0.2.ebuild, -libanssipki-crypto-2.0.1.ebuild:
  Improved prime number generation (featuring LCR)

*libanssipki-crypto-2.0.1-r1 (27 May 2014)

  27 May 2014; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.0.1-r1.ebuild, -libanssipki-crypto-2.0.1.ebuild:
  Fix dependencies, cleanup ebuild and switch to EAPI 5.

*libanssipki-crypto-2.0.1 (27 May 2014)

  27 May 2014; Baptiste Gourdin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.0.1.ebuild,-libanssipki-crypto-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Add namespace LIBANSSIPKI_CRYPTO to prevent collision with OpenSSL
  ASN1_HASH_ALGO ASN1_ENCRYPT_ALGO constructors from DER

  12 Aug 2013; Audrey Dahan <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>:
  Support for PKCS#1.5 padding
  Class RSAKey new methods for private and public exponentiation

  01 Oct 2013; Audrey Dahan <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>:
  RSA Private key from DER string

*libanssipki-crypto-2.0.0 (09 Jan 2012)

  09 Jan 2012; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +libanssipki-crypto-2.0.0,-libanssipki-crypto-1.3.0:
  New version.

  01 Dec 2011; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>:
  Add a function to export the public key easily.

  23 Nov 2011; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>:
  Documented and cleaned some code.

*libanssipki-crypto-1.3.0 (29 Sep 2010)

  29 Sep 2010; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
